VISUAL: Yan, CEO of Looki, introduces the Looki R1. A screen shows "Story Mode" with "Creepy crawly fun" and organized daily moments.
AUDIO: 'Hi, it\'s Yan, CEO of Looky. In August, we introduced Looky R1, a multi-modal AI wearable, for the very first time. Since launch, people have been wearing Looky everyday.'

[00:12] [scene:ui]
VISUAL: A chat interface shows user prompts like "Analyze what I ate today."
AUDIO: 'It organizes your day into clean, meaningful moments through Story Mode. Every morning, your entire day becomes an auto blog, and users started asking Looky questions no other AI could really answer.'

[00:26] [scene:explanation]
VISUAL: Yan explains "Reactive AI" where Looki helps when asked.
AUDIO: 'Analyze what I ate today. Show my family moments this week. Why am so tired today? This is what we call reactive AI. Looky helps when you ask. For many people, it has already changed'

